{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2001648, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "塔塔开才是真民主", "timestamp": 1625587143, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国14亿人，要是大多数人意见一致，那还蛮令人吃惊的", "timestamp": 1625587150, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001661, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "51＞49在任何情况下也比1＞99好", "timestamp": 1625587186, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001662, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人民民主专政就是以工人阶级为首的人民大众对于反动阶级、反动派和反抗社会主义革命的剥削者的专政。民主不是属于少数人的，而是属于绝大多数人的，是属于工人、农民和其他一切劳动人民以及一切拥护社会主义和爱国的人民的。", "timestamp": 1625587201, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001663, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "引用", "timestamp": 1625587214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001667, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果民意要求限制性少数群体的权利怎么办呢", "timestamp": 1625587239, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001672, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001661, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 51个人想枪毙Carol，Carol就得被枪毙", "timestamp": 1625587253, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001674, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001661, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 很多时候49（甚至更少）会因为一些原因觉得自己是99，便会打骂他们认为的“1”。这种情况怎么办呢0", "timestamp": 1625587276, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001674, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 大骂", "timestamp": 1625587293, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001684, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "柏拉图两千年前就在讨论一样的问题了", "timestamp": 1625587310, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001689, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001662, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 怎么算拥护怎么算爱国呢（小声bb", "timestamp": 1625587326, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001694, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001674, "tag": null, "text": "而原因很可能来自于长时间接受的片面的消息让自己陷入固执的信息茧房里", "timestamp": 1625587350, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001689, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 不知道，我只是个搬运工（×", "timestamp": 1625587355, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001699, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001667, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在美国，可以参考宪政；在中国，民意可以被用来当幌子，也可以被强奸", "timestamp": 1625587373, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001701, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另外，启蒙的观点是不是与民主冲突。启蒙意味着精英主义，把民众看做愚昧的群氓，而民主要求遵守大多数人的决定而不是少数人，不论知识的多少", "timestamp": 1625587374, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001718, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "照这样说，估摸想分马云家的💰的人不少，我们合计合计可以投票把💰分了么", "timestamp": 1625587421, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001721, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001684, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 所以柏拉图得出来不要民主要专政的结论，这似乎与现在政治哲学主流不合", "timestamp": 1625587423, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001732, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001699, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 参考宪政是什么意思", "timestamp": 1625587463, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001755, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001718, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 这样似乎是不违背民主原则的", "timestamp": 1625587526, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001782, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议阅读：\n《论法的精神》\n《群己权界论》\n《社会契约论》", "timestamp": 1625587629, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "读完这三本书你再来树洞你会觉得跟你对线的知识水平都太差了", "timestamp": 1625587659, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001797, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "宪法高于民主投票，人的基本权利不能被多数决剥夺", "timestamp": 1625587693, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001805, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001792, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: hhh为什么要读严复的译本", "timestamp": 1625587711, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001806, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001672, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 至少比1直接突突死99好吧", "timestamp": 1625587739, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001808, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就像louis说的那样", "timestamp": 1625587752, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001811, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001797, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 宪法的权威性又何来？如果民主投票推翻或修改了宪法呢", "timestamp": 1625587763, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001816, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001806, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 有时候51和49也会互相突突", "timestamp": 1625587812, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001826, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001811, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 宪法条文可以分成两类，一类是可以修改的；一类是不可以修改的，如宪法保护人的尊严和自由", "timestamp": 1625587876, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001837, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001816, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 从概率上看，1个人突突99的情况多多了。", "timestamp": 1625587929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001861, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001837, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 多数人的意志由什么来约束呢", "timestamp": 1625588031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001879, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001826, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 不可更改的条文权威性又何来？古代有些过时的观念当时也认为是不可更改的。另外，宪法是概括的，解释权也是一个问题", "timestamp": 1625588133, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001915, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001879, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 自然法高于一切，以实定法为名违反自然的行为终究会被追究。马克思讲，宪法作为上层建筑是有历史性的，随着社会进步，宪法对基本权利的保护会逐渐增强", "timestamp": 1625588323, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001925, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001915, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 似乎这种进步会时不时以暴力形式进行", "timestamp": 1625588375, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001941, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001925, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 公民有超越法律的反抗权", "timestamp": 1625588452, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2002073, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2001662, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 人民民主专政是人民对敌人专政，属于多数人对少数人的专政。多数人对少数人的专政范围更广，例如99个人民对1个人民进行专政，这并没有得到宪法的支持。", "timestamp": 1625589125, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2002378, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2002073, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 什么是人民？什么是敌人？只要评判标准在1手上，就是1对99的专政不是吗？", "timestamp": 1625590938, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2002388, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2002378, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 是的，如果实质上如你所说的话", "timestamp": 1625591026, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2002391, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2002378, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 我所说的是形式上的", "timestamp": 1625591043, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2002539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2002378, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不过我觉得以如今的民主形式来看，1说了算还是99说了算都一样。因为今天的民主形式都是选项数量极少的，选项本身就被少数人操纵了，接下来无论怎么投票怎么选都无所谓。", "timestamp": 1625592651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2003430, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2002539, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 专政也不能什么基本权利都不承认吧，那不成文革了？", "timestamp": 1625616688, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2003575, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2003430, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 我不是特别清楚，基本权利大概不是靠民主来保证的吧", "timestamp": 1625619902, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2003580, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 391500, "reply_to": 2003430, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 如果按照宪法，宪法保证公民的基本权利。公民不等于人民，公民范围比人民大，只要具有中国国籍的人就是公民，人民是公民，敌人也是公民，宪法都保障他们的基本权利", "timestamp": 1625620003, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 391500, "reply": 42, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "民主的界限在什么地方，如果大多数人同意剥夺少数人的权利，这算民主吗", "timestamp": 1625587106, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1625620004, "url": "", "vote": {}}}